        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer827072246" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16906408469491655954">An excellent read, combining an exciting detective story with well-told descriptions of South African locales and life before Mandela. It is infuriating to read of the official intolerance and persecution of coloreds and blacks by despicable, hateful whites. This was the first in a series.<br/><br/>My wife and I had the good fortune to meet Malla a couple of years ago at a Key West Literary Seminar. We heard her speak and shared a meal with her. She is a delightful person.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

